<h1 id="chapter-3--functions">Chapter 3 : Functions</h1>
<p>All the questions in this chapter are required to be programmed using functions only.</p>

<ol>
  <li>Write a function to compute the factorial of a number.</li>
  <li>Write a function to compute the GCD of two numbers.</li>
  <li>Write a function to compute the GCD of three numbers.</li>
  <li>Write a function to compute the LCM of two numbers.</li>
  <li>Write a function to accept a list L and return a sorted list.</li>
  <li>The following questions are to be programmed without sorting the list.
    <ul>
      <li>Given a list <em>L</em> find the least element in it.</li>
      <li>Given a list <em>L</em> find the second, third and fourth least elements in it.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Given a list <em>L</em> find the $k$th least element in it.</li>
  <li>Implement the following questions using functions:
    <ul>
      <li>Bubble Sort</li>
      <li>Binary Search</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Implement Merge Sort</li>
  <li>Implement Quick Sort
    <ul>
      <li>Merge Sort</li>
      <li>Quick Sort</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

